Package: KronaR
Title: R Wrapper for Krona Interactive Charts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Valentin", "Shared", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "valentin@example.com")
  )
Description: Generates self-contained, interactive, zoomable hierarchical
    pie charts using the Krona HTML5 visualization engine. Accepts R data frames
    and produces HTML widgets (renderable via iframes) or static PNG snapshots.
